name: SunnySideUp
additional_notices: Kindly be aware of liquidity-related risks. This notice is not directed at any project in particular, and is more of a cautionary reminder.

description.en:
Sunny Side Up is a DeFi protocol built on Solana. We started off as a staking service but have now expanded to do more. 
Our staking strategies allow you to enjoy great returns and a high APY. Our goal is to create opportunities to participate and earn more with DeFi for our users.
